Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Last Updated: Tuesday, October 3, 2024
By installing and using our app, you agree to this privacy policy and give explicit and informed consent to the processing of your information.
How can we collect information?
Requested permissions before installing or using our application:
INTERNET
: Full network access is required to serve advertisements and download images.
NETWORK STATE
: View network connections to allow the app to adjust its behavior based on network connectivity.
STORAGE
: Access to external storage is required to save images and cache images.
SET WALLPAPERS PERMISSION
: Required to set wallpapers directly from the app.
What information do we collect?
Personal Data
Generally, we do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) from you when you download and use our Android applications (e.g., your name, email address). We do not require users to register to use our application, nor do we track visits to our application. Additionally, we do not maintain any server to store such PII.
Non-personal Data
Non-personal data refers to information that, by itself, does not personally identify you. We do not store any such data on our servers.
Ad Serving Technology
We may disclose non-personal data to third parties or allow third parties to collect non-personal data through embedded technology. To deliver ads, third-party advertising companies may place or recognize unique cookies, anonymous identifiers, or similar technology to gather non-personally identifiable information. We use
AdMob
as our advertising provider in the app.
For more information on third-party service providers used by our app, you can visit the following links:
Google Play Services
AdMob
Acceptance of this policy
By using our mobile app or its services, you acknowledge that you have read this policy and agree to all its terms and conditions. If you do not agree to abide by the terms of this policy, you are not authorized to use or access our mobile apps or services.
Contact Us
If you have any concerns or need further information regarding our privacy policy, feel free to email us at
[emailÂ protected]
. We will endeavor to provide clear answers to your questions in a timely manner.
